[04/01/2019 03:05:46] <font color="#ffff00">Londres.</font>
[04/01/2019 03:05:47] <font color="#ffff00">Miami.</font>
[04/01/2019 03:05:50] <font color="#ffff00">Las amenazas provienen del mar.</font>
[04/01/2019 03:05:51] <font color="#ffff00">De arriba...</font>
